---
/**
 * TheProblem — Act II
 * Dark section with line-by-line text reveal
 * 
 * COPY STRATEGY: Validate Sarah's suspicions. She already distrusts the food 
 * system—we're not convincing her of anything new, just confirming what she 
 * already knows. Creates emotional resonance and positions us as allies.
 */
---

<section 
  id="problem" 
  class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-24 bg-[#1a1a1a] text-[#F2F0E9] overflow-hidden"
>
  <!-- Subtle grain overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none">
    <svg class="w-full h-full">
      <filter id="grain">
        <feTurbulence type="fractalNoise" baseFrequency="0.8" numOctaves="4" stitchTiles="stitch" />
      </filter>
      <rect width="100%" height="100%" filter="url(#grain)" />
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12 lg:gap-16">
    <!-- Text Content -->
    <div class="problem-text space-y-8 text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl leading-relaxed font-['EB_Garamond',serif] lg:flex-1">
      <p class="problem-line ">
        You already know something is wrong.
      </p>
      <p class="problem-line ">
        Grocery store chicken is pale, watery, and flavorless. It needs seasoning just to taste like anything.
      </p>
      <p class="problem-line ">
        That's because most birds never see sunlight. They're raised in crowded barns, bred for speed—not nourishment.
      </p>
      <p class="problem-line text-[#C8A97E] font-medium">
        You deserve better. Your family deserves better.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Cornish Cross Chicken Image -->
    <div class="problem-image lg:flex-1 flex justify-center">
      <img 
        src="/cornish-cross.png" 
        alt="Cornish Cross chicken in pasture" 
        loading="lazy"
        class="w-64 h-64 md:w-80 md:h-80 lg:w-96 lg:h-96 object-cover rounded-full shadow-2xl ring-4 ring-[#C8A97E]/20"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


